    <item>
      <title>WAVE Audit No. 1</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/blog/a11y-website/audit-1/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Jun 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/blog/a11y-website/audit-1/</guid>
      <description>&lt;style type=&#34;text/css&#34;&gt;&#xA;.page-main img {&#xA;  box-shadow: 0px 0px 2px 2px rgba( 0, 0, 0, 0.2 );&#xA;  #/* ease | ease-in | ease-out | linear */&#xA;  transition: transform ease-in-out 0.6s;&#xA;}&#xA;&#xA;.page-main img:hover {&#xA;  transform: scale(1.4);&#xA;}&#xA;&lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Did you know that 97.4% of home pages have web accessibility failures???&lt;/strong&gt; :scream:&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This finding is one of many from an accessibility analysis that non-profit WebAIM (Web Accessibility in Mind) conducts annually on home pages of the top one million websites. You can find a summary of these findings in a WebAIM &#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://webaim.org/blog/webaim-million-2021/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;blog post&lt;/a&gt; and detailed information in the &#xA;&lt;a href=&#34;https://webaim.org/projects/million/#wcag&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;full report&lt;/a&gt;, both published on April 30, 2021.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
